BEGIN_PGML

Evaluate the following expressions. If the answer is undefined, type *DNE* (meaning "does not exist").

a)    [`` [$frac0] = ``]  [________]{$ans0} 

b)    [`` [$frac1] = ``]  [________]{$ans1}  

END_PGML

